                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5487" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OM-0228</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8243 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">高效动力，乐享驾趣——看立马电动车如何乘风破浪，精益求远？ </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Efficient power, enjoy the fun of driving——See LIMA  how to ride the wind and waves of electric vehicles, lean seek far?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">苏海涛，袁从瑞，袁壮，修义雨</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南昌大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张和平</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">立马车业集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新国标；精益价值流；线平衡；生产瓶颈；平衡改善；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">New national standard; lean value flow; line balance; production  bottleneck; balance improvement</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">全新的《电动自行车安全技术规范》强制性国家标准于2019年正式实施，新国标确立了电动自行车行业从高速度向高质量发展的主基调。面对全新的行业挑战，成本的增加、技术的升级、产能的爬坡等变化点成为了电动车行业需共同克服的难题。新国标下，机遇与挑战并存，立马车业集团凭借多年来的精益管理经验，重新规划生产端，借助精益生产工具发现问题、分析问题、解决问题，完成转型规模化生产，实现生产线平衡，消除瓶颈，回落企业生产成本，提升企业生产运营管理能力，秉承“改善永无止境”的思想对现有生产制造系统形成改善闭环。面对行业洗牌，立马本着“追求卓越，共创辉煌”的精神，加速自我革新与进化，迎难而上，在市场竞争中占领先机。作为我国电动车行业的标志性品牌，立马车业集团切实做到了快速响应国家政策，尽快适应新国标，不断引领行业发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The new mandatory national standard &quot;E-Bike Safety Technical Specifications&quot; was formally implemented in 2019. The new national standard has established the main tone for the development of the electric bicycle industry from high speed to high quality. In the face of brand-new industry challenges, changes in costs such as increased costs, technological upgrades, and productivity ramp-ups have become problems that the electric vehicle industry needs to overcome together. Under the new national standard, opportunities and challenges coexist. With years of experience in lean management, Lima Vehicle Group re-plans the production side, uses lean production tools to discover, analyze, and solve problems, complete the transformation of large-scale production, achieve production line balance, and eliminate The bottleneck, lowering the production cost of the enterprise, improving the production and operation management ability of the enterprise, and adhering to the idea of &quot;improving never ending&quot; to form a closed-loop improvement of the existing manufacturing system. Facing the industry reshuffle, immediately in line with the spirit of &quot;pursuing excellence and creating brilliance together&quot;, speed up self-innovation and evolution, face difficulties, and take the lead in market competition. As the iconic brand of my country&#39;s electric vehicle industry, Lima Vehicle Group has effectively responded to national policies quickly, adapted to the new national standard as soon as possible, and continuously led the development of the industry.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《运营管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">TOC 理论、精益生产、平衡改善法则</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-09</td>
                            </tr>
